title: Princess Jasmine & Aladdin Sing 'A Whole New World' Again On 'Good Morning America' - Watch Now!
text: It’s safe to say that “A Whole New World” is probably JJJ‘s favorite song ever from the classic Disney movies and seeing the original singers, Brad Kane and Lea Salonga perform it again twenty some years later, is just magic. Lea and Brad reunited with composer Alan Menken, plus voice actors Scott Weinger, Linda Larkin [...] »
